<div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>This query/response is designed for interaction between a client system and an MPI (Master Person Index). The query consists of a set of demographic and/or visit attribute values for a person, and the response is the list of candidates considered by the MPI to match that set.</p>
</div>
<table class="tableblock frame-all grid-all stretch">
